        <item>
            <title>港铁称智能实时监察系统有作用 	4 月曾检测出道岔有损蚀及时维修</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/04/mtr-introduce-2-sets-of-intelligent-real-time-monitoring-system/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mtr-introduce-2-sets-of-intelligent-real-time-monitoring-system</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/07/04/mtr-introduce-2-sets-of-intelligent-real-time-monitoring-system/life-tech/smartcity/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 14:30:19 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅游]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[mtr]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[港铁]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1247808</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">港铁最近引入轨道及车轮智能监测系统，能在行车中不断收集实时数据至数据中心，并通过大数据分析后能及早发现潜在问题，确保有效实施预测性维修。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1247815 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-4-scaled-e1720090327652-694x394.jpg" alt="轨道智能监测系统" width="694" height="394" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-4-scaled-e1720090327652-694x394.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/2-4-scaled-e1720090327652-1280x726.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1247816 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-4-scaled-e1720090349820-694x413.jpg" alt="轨道智能监测系统" width="694" height="413" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-4-scaled-e1720090349820-694x413.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/1-4-scaled-e1720090349820-1280x762.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1247814 size-medium" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-2-scaled-e1720090373622-694x386.jpg" alt="轨道智能监测系统" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-2-scaled-e1720090373622-694x386.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/3-2-scaled-e1720090373622-1280x712.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1760177-20240704.htm?spTabChangeable=0&amp;fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR2EqsQEydsV5iCwJ3OG8VRH7CtpNVSHxIaCiH0fhFVUwI8N1uuJgwziKZs_aem_a5q75cIy4CVC2cFkhgB27g">RTHK</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">港铁表示目前每条铁路线均有两部载客列车装有轨道智能监测系统，列车中的转向架装有大量的震动感应器和激光探测相机，行车时会不断收集数据。港铁车务工程服务及创科总管陈庆强解释，每日载客列车都会经过同一个道岔，其震动程度会被系统收集，当收集的震动幅度与长时间收集的数据有明显差异，就代表道岔存在不正常的损蚀。系统检测到异常便能安排维修人员到现场进行检查和修复，并能以回复震动幅度至正常水平作维修参考。至于港铁自主研发的车轮智能监测系统，去年在荃湾线试用，陈庆强认为其可靠性高且能有效预测潜在异常。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">陈庆强指出港铁在 2023 – 2027 年间会投入超过 10 亿元研发创新科技，并善用资源寻找不同可应用在铁路上的技术，改善预测性维修和提升「黄金两小时」的维修效率，希望能减少日常行车可能对乘客造成的影响。系统今年 4 月曾经发挥作用，在东铁线一个道岔，发现震动幅度有上升趋势，随后发现道岔有损蚀，经维修处理后，震动下降至可接受水平。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">资料来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1760177-20240704.htm?spTabChangeable=0&amp;fbclid=IwZXh0bgNhZW0CMTAAAR2EqsQEydsV5iCwJ3OG8VRH7CtpNVSHxIaCiH0fhFVUwI8N1uuJgwziKZs_aem_a5q75cIy4CVC2cFkhgB27g">RTHK</a></p><p>图片来源：<a href="https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1760211-20240704.htm">RTHK</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/18/mtr-5/life-tech/smartcity/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">港铁提升 24 个车站 5G 网络服务　天后站今天率先启用</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/09/mtr-can-update-in-28-hours/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">港铁：28 小时内可完成更新    7 月 28 日停观塘线太子至何文田站</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/07/04/mtr-introduce-2-sets-of-intelligent-real-time-monitoring-system/life-tech/smartcity/">港铁称智能实时监察系统有作用 	4 月曾检测出道岔有损蚀及时维修</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
