            <description>
                <![CDATA[
<p>日本漫画家谏山创的人气漫画作品《进击的巨人》连载 12 年终于迎来结局，早前动画版亦已正式播映完毕，相信各位粉丝都大感不舍，。如果你是巨人粉丝的话，就不容错过小编今日介绍的《进击的巨人》机械键盘套装。全新机械键盘套装即日起接受预订，实物将于香港动漫电玩节 2024 〈动漫联动〉摊位展出、公开发售，预订了的朋友也可进场取货。现在就让小编开箱先睹为快，和大家看看这套机械键盘。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245806" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09708-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09708-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09708.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>《进击的巨人》机械键盘由台湾机械键盘品牌 Ducky 制造，采用 Ducky One 2 RGB 108 键规格，搭载 PBT 热升华键帽和德国 Cherry MX 机械茶轴，更有多达 8 种背光模式，而且配有 3 段式调整高度脚架，方便用家调节至适合自己的高度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245808" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09709-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09709-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09709.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245897" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09739-2-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09739-2-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09739-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲ 搭载德国 Cherry MX 机械茶轴</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1245876" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09734-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09734-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/kan09734.jpg